<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٠٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7010">يَحْيَى: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2521">أَبِي حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2676">سَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«التَّسْبِيحُ لِلرِّجَالِ، وَالتَّصْفِيحُ لِلنِّسَاءِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>